<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Learnly</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kode+Mono:wght@400..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Kode Mono', 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif !important;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .header img {
            max-width: 50px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 20px 20px 0px 20px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 8px 20px 15px 20px;
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .cta,
        .content a {
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999999;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #0070f3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .headerLogoText {
            font-size: 35px;
            color: #333333;
            font-family: 'Kode Mono', 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif !important;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
        }

        ::selection {
            color: #000000;
            background: #d1d1d1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <!-- <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/71/Vercel_logo_black.svg" alt="Vercel Logo"> -->
            <h1 class="headerLogoText">LEARNLY.</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="greeting">
            Hello, {{name}}
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Welcome to Learnly!</p>
            <p>We are excited to have you on board. Our platform is designed to provide you with the best learning
                experience.</p>
            <p>To get started, please click the button below:</p>
            <a href="{{verify_link}}" class="cta">Verify Account</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="{{support_link}}">contact our support team</a>.</p>
            <p><a href="{{manage_notifications_link}}">Manage your notification settings</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>